## Sub-areas completed

### A. CSV shipment import ‚Äî DONE
- New page: `src/app/(platform)/platform/shipments/import/page.tsx` with drag-drop CSV uploader, preview table, error reporting, and commit button.
- Downloadable template: GET `/api/shipments/import` returns `shipments-template.csv` with canonical 11-column header and a sample row.
- Import API: POST `/api/shipments/import` (auth-gated). Accepts multipart, JSON, or raw CSV. `?dryRun=1` returns a preview with per-row validation errors. Without dryRun, validates and bulk-inserts scoped to `session.user.orgId`. Refuses to insert if any row is invalid.
