- New queries file `src/lib/db/queries/shipments.ts`: `getShipmentsByOrg(orgId)`, `createShipment(data)`, `bulkInsertShipments(rows)`, `getOrgDemoFlag(orgId)`.
- Generated initial drizzle migration at `drizzle/0000_milky_hellcat.sql` (covers entire current schema; this was the first generated migration in this repo).

### E. Demo mode separation ‚Äî DONE
- Added `isDemo` boolean to `organizations` table, default false.
- Renamed `src/lib/data/dashboard.ts` -> `src/lib/data/demo-data.ts`. The old path is now a re-export shim so the 11 existing component imports keep compiling without churn.
